# Artifacts Directory

This directory contains generated outputs from the ranking pipeline.

## Contents (auto-generated)

- `submission.csv` — Final top-100 submission CSV
- `full_score_breakdown.csv` — All feature scores for top candidates
- `validation_report.json` — Schema validation results
- `suspicious_profiles.csv` — Medium/high-risk integrity profiles
- `embeddings.npy` — Optional precomputed candidate embeddings (float16)
- `embedding_ids.json` — Candidate ID order for embeddings

## Notes

- All files in this directory are gitignored except `.gitkeep`
- Re-run `rank.py` or use the Streamlit "Run Ranking" page to regenerate
